reviews.review_text:
A Great Show I saw most of the east coast shows from around '82 ~ '90. I thought the Providence shows always rocked. This copy of the show sounds better than the other ones, less 'muddy'.

Uh, I guess this is as good a place as any to say 'Thank You' to Jerry and all the Boys. Somehow, the love got through my dead and de-sensitized heart and filled it with gratitude..  even today I can still see Love and Beauty in this world... Anyway, go ahead and listen...
Spring Fling Solid sound and show..Love the 1st set from this one~! Give It A Whirl>>Forever Grateful>Forever Dead
